Store Controller - Carrefour (PT Trans Retail Indonesia)
Store Controller  -
Store Controller
Responsibilities
Ensure all activities related to data management, sales transaction document or other activity that is received from every department run well.Monitor incomes and expenses from and to store run according to the procedures.Managing, evaluating and reporting implementation of Financial procedures at store.Managing, evaluating and reporting activities which are related to stock adjustment. Job Requirements:Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor's Degree in Finance/Accountancy/Banking or equivalent.At least 2 years of working experience in the related field is required for this position. Preferably Supervisor / Coordinators specializing in Finance - General/Cost Accounting, Auditor or equivalent.Job role in Management or equivalentExcellent in Accounting and ReportingComputer literateWilling to join immediately Please send your complete resume & recent photograph to: human_resources@transretail.co.idand mention your available city / location
